captures the enigma that Maradona was - part villain, part genius.

00:02:27.401 --> 00:02:32.701
It was the 22nd of June 1986, in Mexico City.

00:02:33.841 --> 00:02:39.981
Over 110,000 people were packed into the Azteca Stadium to watch the

00:02:39.981 --> 00:02:44.061
World Cup quarter final between England and Maradona’s Argentina.

00:02:45.441 --> 00:02:49.341
After a goalless first half, six minutes into the

00:02:49.341 --> 00:02:52.841
second half of the match Argentina were on the attack.

00:02:54.001 --> 00:02:57.701
