00:04:16.481 --> 00:04:20.541
little with the head of Maradona and a little with the hand of God.”

00:04:21.791 --> 00:04:26.474
Still furious about Maradona’s cheating, minutes later the England players and fans could

00:04:26.561 --> 00:04:32.261
do nothing as the little Argentinian dribbled around almost the entire England team and

00:04:32.261 --> 00:04:37.391
scored what is widely considered to be the greatest goal in the history of football.

00:04:38.721 --> 00:04:42.241
Within the space of a few minutes, the world had seen the

00:04:42.291 --> 00:04:46.621
two sides of Diego Maradona - the villain and the genius.

